==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la}} {{term|futurus|futūrus|lang=la}}, irregular future active participle of {{term|sum||I am|lang=la}}, from {{proto|Indo-European|bhū-||bheu-|to become, be|lang=en}}. Cognate with {{etyl|ang|-}} {{term|beo|bēo|I become, I will be, I am|lang=ang}}. More at {{l|en|be}}.

